text: Wendy Farrington (born 1 December 1941) is a British alpine skier. She competed at the 1960 Winter Olympics and the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:British female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Great Britain Category:Alpine skiers at the 1960 Winter Olympics Category:Alpine skiers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:People from Knaresborough
